</P>
<P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><BR>
</P>
<P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; font-weight: medium"><FONT FACE="arial, sans-serif"><FONT SIZE=2>New
in version 1.265 (02/16/11): </FONT></FONT>
</P>
<UL>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; font-weight: medium"><FONT FACE="arial, sans-serif"><FONT SIZE=2>Added
	option in gassst_to_sam to output multiple results per read in the
	sam format, not only the best one.</FONT></FONT></P>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; font-weight: medium"><FONT FACE="arial, sans-serif"><FONT SIZE=2>Support
	for even larger reads.</FONT></FONT></P>
</UL>
<P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><BR>
</P>
<P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><BR>
</P>
<P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; font-weight: medium"><FONT FACE="arial, sans-serif"><FONT SIZE=2>Bugs
corrected in version 1.262 (10/21/10): </FONT></FONT>
</P>
<UL>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; font-weight: medium"><FONT FACE="arial, sans-serif"><FONT SIZE=2>bug
	in sam format generation causing read sequences to be sometimes
	erroneously reversed when it should not and vice-versa.</FONT></FONT></P>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; font-weight: medium"><FONT FACE="arial, sans-serif"><FONT SIZE=2>fixed
	crashes for extra long ( &gt; 1000 nt ) reads.</FONT></FONT></P>
</UL>
<P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><BR>
</P>
<P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; font-weight: medium"><FONT FACE="arial, sans-serif"><FONT SIZE=2>New
in version 1.24 : </FONT></FONT>
</P>
<UL>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; font-weight: medium"><FONT FACE="arial, sans-serif"><FONT SIZE=2>added
	support for processors without ssse3 (-amd flag at compilation)</FONT></FONT></P>
</UL>
<P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in"><BR>
</P>
<P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; font-weight: medium"><FONT FACE="arial, sans-serif"><FONT SIZE=2>New
in version 1.23 : </FONT></FONT>
</P>
<UL>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; font-weight: medium"><FONT FACE="arial, sans-serif"><FONT SIZE=2>added
	tool to convert to sam format.</FONT></FONT></P>
	<LI><P ALIGN=LEFT STYLE="margin-bottom: 0in; font-weight: medium"><FONT FACE="arial, sans-serif"><FONT SIZE=2>Automatic
	seed length calculation.</FONT></FONT></P>
</UL>
